Subject: Re: [T2] Caliper differences

On Mon, 31 Mar 2008, Martin Jr., D. Michael wrote:

> Just wondering what the differences are in the front disc calipers on a 1971
> and a 1976?

> I am having trouble with the front calipers on my 1971 Westy but have a 1976
> transporter I have been using for parts.

The calipers are different and cannot be interchanged without also
swapping the spindles, disks, etc.  Since you have a parts bus just pop
the spindles off at the ball joints and swap the whole assembly.

George
